11. a. Write a program
for creating a pie-chart in R using the input vector (21,62,10,53). Provide
labels for the chart as ‘London’, ‘New York’, ‘Singapore’, ‘Mumbai’. Add a
title to the chart as ‘city pie-chart’ and add a legend at the top right corner
of the chart.


program :

x <- c(21, 62, 10, 53)
labels <- c("London", "New York", "Singapore", "Mumbai")

pie(x,labels)

png(file = “city.jpg”)

dev.off()
